{"tid":116232,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加呼籲阿迷向倫敦二哥學野","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T20:54:19.000Z","uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b68cfd1573e584bb281bd53db7ea7f7bf8781c7d","tid":116232,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C4Qc5g1WYAEHd2F.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC4Qc5g1WYAEHd2F.jpg%20&h=30ed1891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加籲擁躉團結遭回嗆：阿仙奴球迷是全球最忠誠 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在英超連敗兩仗的阿仙奴，星期六將於主場迎戰近兩場分別賽和曼聯和擊敗利物浦的侯城。上周作客車路士被技術性擊倒，有兵工球迷於史丹福橋舉起「受夠」的標語，要求執教二十年的領隊雲加，今夏約滿後離隊，亦有球迷表示，本周不會入場支持阿仙奴。 <br />\n<br />\n雲加呼籲球迷團結，又用北倫敦死敵熱刺做例子，指對方擁躉一直對球隊不離不棄，阿仙奴球迷亦應一樣。他又說雖然目前落後榜首的車路士十二分，但現在放棄是太早。 <br />\n<br />\n有球迷在網上留言回應雲加的「忠誠論」，表示全世界最忠誠的正正是阿仙奴球迷，他們經歷多年失望和痛苦，依然對球隊從一而終，要反省的應是雲加本人。亦有球迷拿出數據，指雲加是全球最高薪八位「教頭」中，唯一一位過往十年沒贏過本土聯賽或歐聯錦標。"},{"pid":"934798bc2b97fe47112961f608d90bb7b6239e63","tid":116232,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C4Qc5g1WYAEHd2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC4Qc5g1WYAEHd2F.jpg&h=11ce5579&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5544bf272adc8904ab986b1f76bf5711fb30039c","tid":116232,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"二哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1e367a2bf9a328f695b4f196ef3c04b6121c53","tid":116232,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9461ab3852a3dbe2808e1b999c4eeb4d97d0886c","tid":116232,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170c9a213dd16e9c187b6987b4cdb8986a2a5c38","tid":116232,"uid":5708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:54:19.000Z","msg":"Agger"}]}